Package: proActiv
Title: Estimate Promoter Activity from RNA-Seq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Deniz",
           family = "Demircioglu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ddemircioglu@gis.a-star.edu.sg",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7857-0407"))
Description: Estimate promoter activity using RNA-Seq data. 
  This package uses Tophat2 or STAR junction files and estimates promoter activity. 
  The promoters of each gene can be identified by providing a txdb object for the input annotation version. 
